channel.title: I need help with making a teleport in the magic tab
channel.description:
Hey guys,
Say I want to click on Lumbridge teleport in my magic tab and it takes me to Karamja. How would I do that?
I know i need to know the coords of the place, but i need to know what the rest of it is and [b]WHERE TO PUT IT.[/b]
So if anyone know, please inform me. :D
